articles.title: French Open: Novak Djokovic defeats Roberto Carballes Baena in straight sets to reach third round at Roland Garros - Sky Sports
articles.description: Novak Djokovic won 14 of the last 17 games to comfortably dispose of Roberto Carballes Baena in straight sets in their second-round clash at the French Open.
